task.summary: Initial commit of NobleTools to github
Added pom.xml and re-organized the project a bit

Refactored Mention to allow multiple Modifiers of the same type. Added different colors to anchors and modifiers in NobleMentions HTML output When creating new ontologies with local file import, setup IRI mapper to look into local directory for other dependencies
Added an ability to find annotation to annotation relationships
Filter upgraded numbers when they are attached to variables
modified addModifierInstance() method to account for the fact that a same thing can be added using more specific property

implemented AnnotationEvaluation weighted score NobleMentions should now process headers as well NobleMentions now tries to re-validate failed variables if they contain an equivalent annotation relation

implemented AnnotationEvaluation weighted score NobleMentions should now process headers as well NobleMentions now tries to re-validate failed variables if they contain an equivalent annotation relation Added Analysis object for storing analysis
Integrated AttributeWeights into AnnotationEvaluation Added visualization option to AnnotationEvaluation Added useful Span object
